title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fianc√© plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Yugpurush
subTitle: Anirudh is discharged from an asylum after 20 years of treatment. Although he still struggles to adjust to the normal world, he finds comfort with Sunita.

title: Sau Din Saas Ke
subTitle: Durga marries Prakash, unaware of his mother Bhawani Devi's dominating and abusive nature. She later insists on moving in with his family in order to teach Bhawani Devi a lesson.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Kachche Dhaage
subTitle: Stepbrothers Aftab and Jai, who loathe each other, must learn to put aside their differences and work together to prove their innocence in a terrorism case.

title: Sapne Saajan Ke
subTitle: Shalini, who has always wanted her daughter, Jyoti, to marry a rich man, is happy that she has found Deepak to be her life partner. However, no one knows that he is only pretending to be wealthy.

title: Gharwali Baharwali
subTitle: Arun inadvertently ties the knot with Manisha and even has a child with her. He keeps this a secret from his first wife Kaajal. It is only a matter of time before his life starts to unravel.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Zulm Ki Hukumat
subTitle: Swami, a gangster who poses as a god-man, develops enmity with Pitambar and kills him. Enraged, Pitambar's youngest brother, Pratap, decides to avenge his death.

title: NISHANT - The Night's End
subTitle: After his wife Rukmini is abducted by his cruel brother, Vishwam is forced to confront the deep-rooted issues of power and control that plague their village, leading to tragic consequences.

title: Tarazu
subTitle: Ram Yadav, an honest police officer, earns the wrath of Appa Rao, an influential man, when he arrests the latter's criminal son.

title: Meri Jung
subTitle: Deepak Verma lives happily with his family, but things change when he is prosecuted by Thakral for murder. His son, Arun, vows to exact revenge against Thakral and prove his father's innocence.

title: Swarag Se Sunder
subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Rakshak
subTitle: ASP Raj Sinha is assigned to catch the criminal responsible for printing and circulating fake currency notes. However, he is shocked to learn that the person is none other than his childhood friend.

title: Ajnabee
subTitle: Raj and Priya befriend their new neighbours Vicky and Sonia. One day, Raj wakes up in Vicky's house and finds out that Sonia is killed and he is framed for it.

title: Ajnabee

title: Dulhan Banu Main Teri
subTitle: Deepak, a wealthy expatriate, faces family opposition as he pursues a romance with Radha, a woman from humble origins, whilst navigating cultural expectations and class divides.

title: Ram Aur Shyam
subTitle: Ram escapes from his home when he learns that his abusive brother-in-law plans to kill him. Justice is meted out when Shyam, Ram's long-lost twin, accidentally takes his place.

title: Sohni Mahiwal
subTitle: Mirza falls in love with Sohni, the daughter of a potter but their relationship is not accepted and he is thrown out of the village. Later, he starts meeting her disguised as a shepherd.

title: M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story
subTitle: M S Dhoni, a boy from Ranchi, aspires to play cricket for India. Though he initially tries to please his father by working for the Indian Railways, he ultimately decides to chase his dreams.

title: Mujrim
subTitle: Yashoda, a widow, brings up her children with love and honesty. However, she is disappointed when her son Shankar is arrested for breaking the law and disowns him.

title: Yeshwant
subTitle: Yeshwant, an honest police inspector, is framed and arrested for a murder. However, after being released from prison, he learns that his wife is having an affair.

title: Ziddi
subTitle: Deva, a vigilant young man, quickly climbs amongst the ranks of criminals in his city. However, things get complicated when he is framed for the assassination attempt of the CM.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Twins Amit and Kishan are separated at birth. However, when their paths cross in the future, together they work their way through and strive to overcome challenges.
